This was a fantastic recipe. Great for using up fresh tomatoes. I didn't have any dry white wine on hand so I used Strongbow dry cider instead and it turned out great! I caramelized my onions slightly which also added a nice hint of sweet. The green olives totally add that zing that the fish needs.

