Rating: 3
This tasted good and was easy to make. I used chopped onions (as the tester suggested), but they didn't cook enough. Should have sauteed them first, or used the pearl onions as the recipe had. It also seemed salty enough without adding extra salt for seasoning, probably because the olives I used were packed in brine. Double garlic as the tester suggested (which I did) was also a good idea.